@node Reqs
XI.  Requirements

    Questions2.1 was compiled and runs on my A500
with 1 Meg Chip and 1 1/2 Fast running OS 2.1.	I
believe it takes up about 750K of memory (yikes!)
due to its graphic intensive GUI.  @{"(See Future)" link Future 13}
It should work on earlier OS's, but will require
that extra RAM.







